des: From Casinos to historical land marks, Biloxi, MS , is a great place to think about when traveling near the gulf coast. This skill will help user learn about the history and culture of the south and at the same time, relax at beautiful beaches. If you're an indoor type, casino and hotel services are at your finger tip. Users can also ask about local news provided by the New York Times.
